&nbsp;
Vanacore, according to a first reconstruction of the incident based on testimonies, had to reach a hospital ward, that of cardiology, and would have an altercation with the sworn guards > because&nbsp; wanted to use his car to move in the avenues surrounding the different pavilions of the structure. The sixty-year-old had a malore during the fight and was rescued and admitted, but died shortly after. The prosecutor opened an investigation file and delegated to the carabinieri the investigations

